      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BODAK YELLOW (4) lines up here off a comfortable win at this track after jumping from box 7 (17.33). Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Well placed and can measure up. ROAD RAGE GUNDI (7) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 2.75 lengths (17.71). Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has ability and is one of the better chances. NITRO'S IZZY (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (17.60) in a Novice race at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Well placed here and should do much better. CASH TO FLAMES (1) is worth including.",
